@page "/docs"

<PageTitle>GuideFlow - Documentation</PageTitle>

<div class="docs-content">
    <h1>Getting Started</h1>
    <p class="docs-lead">
        GuideFlow is a Blazor component library for building accessible, animated guided tours.
        Follow the steps below to add it to your project.
    </p>

    <h2 id="installation">
        Installation
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#installation">#</a>
    </h2>

    <p>Install the NuGet package:</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="bash" Code="dotnet add package GuideFlow" />

    <h2 id="setup">
        Setup
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#setup">#</a>
    </h2>

    <p>Register the service in <code>Program.cs</code>:</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="razor" Code="builder.Services.AddGuideFlow();" />

    <p>Add the CSS and JS to your <code>index.html</code> or <code>_Host.cshtml</code>:</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="html" Code="@(@"<link href=""_content/GuideFlow/guideflow.css"" rel=""stylesheet"" />
<script src=""_content/GuideFlow/guideflow.module.js""></script>")" />

    <h2 id="first-tour">
        Your First Tour
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#first-tour">#</a>
    </h2>

    <p>Wrap your page content with <code>GuideFlowTour</code> and add steps:</p>

    <CodeBlock Language="razor" Code="@(@"<GuideFlowTour TourOptions=""@options"">
    <GuideFlowStep Selector=""#step1"" Title=""Welcome!"" Order=""0"">
        <p>This is the first step.</p>
    </GuideFlowStep>

    <GuideFlowStep Selector=""#step2"" Title=""Next"" Order=""1"">
        <p>Click here to continue.</p>
    </GuideFlowStep>
</GuideFlowTour>

@code {
    private TourOptions options = new()
    {
        Overlay = true,
        ShowProgress = true,
    };
}")" />

    <div class="docs-note docs-note--info">
        <strong>💡 Two ways to build tours</strong> GuideFlow supports both <strong>declarative</strong> (Razor markup) and <strong>programmatic</strong> (C# fluent API) approaches. See <a href="docs/programmatic-tour">Programmatic Tour</a> for details.
    </div>

    <h2 id="next-steps">
        Next Steps
        <a class="docs-anchor" href="#next-steps">#</a>
    </h2>

    <ul>
        <li><a href="docs/configuration">Configuration</a> - Tour options and customization</li>
        <li><a href="docs/api">API Reference</a> - Full component and service API</li>
        <li><a href="docs/theming">Theming</a> - Light, dark, and custom themes</li>
        <li><a href="docs/animated-tour">Animated Tour</a> - Interactive demo</li>
    </ul>
</div>
